OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoyal Mail to axe up to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F6,000 jobs as losses rise  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Royal Mail has announced plans to make 
OL,6, up to 6,000 people redundant by next   
OL,7, August, blaming ongoing strike action  
OL,8, and rising losses at the business.     
OL,10,FThe postal company said it had begun   
OL,11,Fnotifying workers of its plan, which   
OL,12,Faims to reduce its overall headcount by
OL,13,Fa total of 10,000.                     
OL,15,FThe majority of the cuts will be made  
OL,16,Fthrough redundancy while the rest will 
OL,17,Fbe achieved through natural attrition. 
OL,19,FRoyal Mail also said it expects its    
OL,20,Ffull-year losses to hit #350m.         
